Preamble: - To the aforesaid No. The Government of Maharashtra has approved the establishment of Maharashtra State Sanskrit, Telugu, Bengali and Gor Banjara Sahitya Academy as per the Government Decision No. 1. The issue in this Government Decision No. According to 06, the government was considering creating a compulsory accounting title for all Sahitya Akademi expenditures and 04 Programme Accounting Titles for each of the 04 new Akademi.

Government Decision: - The following new head of accounts are being sanctioned in pursuance of the separate availability of funds under the Programme Expenditure for Maharashtra State Sanskrit, Telugu, Bengali and Gor Banjara Sahitya Akademi Scheme and under the Compulsory Expenditure for all Maharashtra State Hindi, Sindhi, Gujarati, Sanskrit, Telugu, Bengali and Gor Banjara Sahitya Akademi.
